t-1\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_6 + "\" alt=\"Small Image\" class=\"inline-block mt-10 mb-2\" style=\"height:100px;width:auto;\" data-v-c4856c06><h1 class=\"mt-5 text-6xl font-bold leadi sm:text-4xl xl:max-w-3xl font-inter\" data-v-c4856c06> Security of a Fort, <br data-v-c4856c06>Protection like a Porcupine </h1><p class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-4 text-2xl font-inter\" data-v-c4856c06> Fortcupine is a standalone device that enables health facilities to manage and securely store their medical records both on-site and remotely via the internet. Since the facility owns the device, they have full control and ownership of their data, accessible 24/7. It’s a plug-and-play solution that’s easy to use, ensuring seamless integration into any workflow. </p><img src=\"" + _imports_8 + "\" alt=\"Centered Image\" class=\"mt-0 w-100\" data-v-c4856c06></div><div class=\"container flex flex-col items-center max-w-md p-6 mx-auto text-gray-900 bg-white lg:max-w-5xl rounded-3xl\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_6 + "\" alt=\"Small Image\" class=\"inline-block mt-10 mb-2\" style=\"height:100px;width:auto;\" data-v-c4856c06><h1 class=\"mt-5 text-6xl font-bold leadi sm:text-3xl xl:max-w-4xl font-inter\" data-v-c4856c06> Why Fortcupine? </h1></div><div id=\"why-fortcupine\" class=\"pt-1 pb-5 text-xs text-neutral-600\" style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-5\" style=\"font-family:Arial, sans-serif;\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_9 + "\" alt=\"No Subscription\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> No Subscription </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> requires no subscription - no monthly fees, no hidden costs. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_10 + "\" alt=\"Works Offline\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Works Offline </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> work anywhere even without an internet connection. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_11 + "\" alt=\"Own Your Data\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Own Your Data </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06> With <b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine ,</b> your data stays with you, fully controlled and always accessible. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_12 + "\" alt=\"Own the Software\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Own the Software </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> gives you full ownership, so you control the software without relying on external providers. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_13 + "\" alt=\"Compliant\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Compliant </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> are built to meet industry standards and regulations, ensuring compliance and peace of mind. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_14 + "\" alt=\"True Privacy\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> True Privacy </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> keep your data private, with no third-party access or unnecessary sharing. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_15 + "\" alt=\"Secure\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Secure </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> provide robust security features that protect your data from breaches and unauthorized access. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_16 + "\" alt=\"Powerful\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Powerful </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> are equipped with advanced tools to handle all your healthcare needs efficiently. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_17 + "\" alt=\"Fast\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Fast </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> deliver lightning-fast performance, free from server lag or internet slowdowns. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_18 + "\" alt=\"Collaborate\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Collaborate </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> allow seamless collaboration while keeping your data secure and private. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_19 + "\" alt=\"Synchronize\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Synchronize </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> sync your data across all your devices effortlessly, ensuring everything is up-to-date. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_20 + "\" alt=\"Decentralized\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Decentralized </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> are decentralized, meaning no single point of failure—your data is always within your reach. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 mb-20 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_21 + "\" alt=\"Open\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Open </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> are built on an open-source foundation, allowing for customization and transparency. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_22 + "\" alt=\"Affordable\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Affordable </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> are designed to be cost-effective, making advanced healthcare technology accessible to everyone. </p></div></div><div class=\"w-full px-4 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"max-w-xs p-5 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_23 + "\" alt=\"Freedom\" class=\"w-40 mx-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><h3 class=\"mt-4 mb-2 text-2xl font-medium text-center text-sky-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Freedom </h3><p class=\"text-base text-center\" data-v-c4856c06><b class=\"font-bold\" data-v-c4856c06>Fortcupine </b> give you the freedom to use the software your way, with no restrictions or vendor lock-in. </p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"container max-w-xl p-6 py-12 mx-auto mb-20 space-y-24 bg-amber-100 lg:px-8 lg:max-w-5xl rounded-3xl\" data-v-c4856c06><div id=\"local-first\" data-v-c4856c06><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-center tracki sm:text-5xl text-neutral font-inter\" data-v-c4856c06> What is Local-First? </h2><p class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-4 text-xl text-center font-inter\" data-v-c4856c06> Local-First is a software paradigm that ensures data stays on users’ devices, offering full control, privacy, and offline access. Unlike cloud-based systems that rely on third-party servers, Local-First combines the local storage of the pre-cloud era with modern sync capabilities, enabling seamless collaboration without sacrificing data ownership. </p><div class=\"grid w-full max-w-5xl grid-cols-1 gap-4 mx-auto mt-10 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"w-full h-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_24 + "\" alt=\"Image 1\" class=\"object-cover w-full h-full border border-gray-200\" data-v-c4856c06></div><div class=\"w-full h-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_25 + "\" alt=\"Image 2\" class=\"object-cover w-full h-full border border-gray-200\" data-v-c4856c06></div><div class=\"w-full h-auto\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_26 + "\" alt=\"Image 3\" class=\"object-cover w-full h-full border border-gray-200\" data-v-c4856c06></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center mt-20\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_27 + "\" alt=\"Ink &amp; Switch Paper\" class=\"inline-block my-2\" style=\"height:auto;width:600px;\" data-v-c4856c06><p class=\"max-w-xl mx-auto mt-4 text-xl text-justify text-neutral-600\" data-v-c4856c06> The concept was introduced in a 2019 whitepaper by Ink &amp; Switch titled <a href=\"https://www.inkandswitch.com/local-first/\" class=\"underline text-sky-600\" target=\"_blank\" data-v-c4856c06>&quot;Local-first software: You own your data, in spite of the cloud.&quot;</a> , a pivotal document outlining seven key principles. <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06></p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center mt-10\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_28 + "\" alt=\"Wired Mag Local-First\" class=\"inline-block my-2\" style=\"height:auto;width:600px;\" data-v-c4856c06><p class=\"max-w-xl mx-auto mt-4 text-xl text-center text-neutral-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Even Wired Magazine featured an <a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/the-cloud-is-a-prison-can-the-local-first-software-movement-set-us-free/\" class=\"underline text-sky-600\" target=\"_blank\" data-v-c4856c06>article</a> on Local-First <br data-v-c4856c06>(August 2023). </p></div></div></div><div class=\"container max-w-xl p-6 mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl\" id=\"our-story\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"text-center\" id=\"our_story\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_6 + "\" alt=\"Small Image\" class=\"inline-block mt-20 mb-2\" style=\"height:100px;width:auto;\" data-v-c4856c06><h2 class=\"mt-5 text-3xl font-bold tracki sm:text-5xl font-inter\" data-v-c4856c06> Our Story </h2><img src=\"" + _imports_29 + "\" alt=\"local first health team image\" class=\"inline-block mt-5\" style=\"height:300px;width:auto;\" data-v-c4856c06><p class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-10 text-xl text-justify text-neutral-600\" data-v-c4856c06> Our team has been developing health record systems since 2016. Even before the local-first concept was introduced in 2019, we were building offline functionality with our own ‘Syncbase’ technology, integrated into our health app, <a href=\"https://www.mycure.md\" class=\"underline text-sky-600\" target=\"_blank\" data-v-c4856c06>&quot;MYCURE.&quot;</a> Over the past 8+ years, we&#39;ve encountered the challenges in this sector and experienced firsthand the limitations of a cloud-based setup. <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06> Before relocating to San Francisco, I traveled extensively across the Philippines, Indonesia, Ethiopia, Kenya, South Africa, India, Sri Lanka, and other countries to observe the difficulties faced by doctors, small clinics, and communtiy drugstores, particularly in developing regions. Many still rely on paper-based or outdated systems, highlighting a stark reality: health equity remains a significant global issue. <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06> Health equity, a top priority for organizations like the World Health Organization (WHO), is about ensuring fair and just access to healthcare for all individuals, regardless of socio-economic status, ethnicity, gender, or geographic location. A critical aspect of this is the ability to access and manage medical records. Yet, in many low- and middle-income countries and marginalized communities, disparities in health outcomes persist due to limited or outdated systems that hinder access to vital health information. <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06> We believe that &#39;Local-First Health&#39; is the solution to these persistent issues. By putting data ownership and management back into the hands of healthcare providers and patients, LFH aims to bridge the gap in healthcare accessibility, empowering underserved communities with secure, offline-capable solutions. <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06> It’s time to finally solve the holy grail of healthcare data and contribute to a world where health equity is more than just an aspiration—it’s a reality. <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06> The future is now—and it’s local. <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06> Dale David<br data-v-c4856c06> Founder<br data-v-c4856c06> Local-First Health <br data-v-c4856c06> San Francisco, CA <br data-v-c4856c06> localfirsthealth@gmail.com <br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06><a href=\"https://x.com/localfirsthlth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display:inline-block;\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_30 + "\" alt=\"Substack Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" data-v-c4856c06></a><a href=\"https://localfirsthealth.substack.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin-left:20px;\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_31 + "\" alt=\"Substack Icon\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" data-v-c4856c06></a></p><p class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4 text-xl text-justify text-neutral-600\" data-v-c4856c06> PS - I participated in the first Local-First Conference, recently held in Berlin, Germany (May 2024). This movement is indeed growing. Re-live the energy of the conference in a <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cLuX0AFNJzQ\" class=\"underline text-sky-600\" target=\"_blank\" data-v-c4856c06>96-second video.</a><br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06></p><br data-v-c4856c06><br data-v-c4856c06></div></div><footer class=\"px-4 divide-y\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center py-6\" data-v-c4856c06><img src=\"" + _imports_6 + "\" alt=\"Fortcupine Logo\" class=\"w-auto h-10 mb-2\" data-v-c4856c06><div class=\"text-sm text-center\" data-v-c4856c06>Born in San Francisco, CA</div><div class=\"text-sm text-center\" data-v-c4856c06>localfirsthealth@gmail.com</div><div class=\"text-sm text-center\" data-v-c4856c06> © 2024 Fortcupine | All rights reserved. </div></div></footer>", 8)

